<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../166/8166.xml">
Devon</link></county>
, South West <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
England</link></country>
.<p>

He was <link>
writer-in-residence</link> at <building wordnetid="102913152" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../548/2116548.xml">
Shakespeare's Globe</link></building>
