<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/17867.xml">
London</link></village>
, for whom he wrote three new plays. He is currently <link>
Playwright-in-Residence</link> at the <theater wordnetid="104417809" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../731/2249731.xml">
